  "grammar": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Grammar Spot",
      "content": "• Question words: What, Where, Who, When, Why, How\n• Object pronouns: me, you, him, her, it, us, them\n• this (near) / that (far)\n• Adjectives: beautiful, big, small, new, old, expensive, cheap, lovely, horrible, hot, cold, friendly, delicious, comfortable"
    },
    "ja": {
      "title": "文法のポイント",
      "content": "• 疑問詞: What, Where, Who, When, Why, How\n• 目的格代名詞: me, you, him, her, it, us, them\n• this（近く）/ that（遠く）\n• 形容詞: 美しい、大きい、小さい、新しい、古い、高い、安い、素敵な、ひどい、暑い、寒い、親切な、美味しい、快適な"
    },
    "fr": {
      "title": "Point de Grammaire",
      "content": "• Mots interrogatifs: What, Where, Who, When, Why, How\n• Pronoms objets: me, you, him, her, it, us, them\n• this (proche) / that (loin)\n• Adjectifs: beau, grand, petit, neuf, vieux, cher, bon marché, magnifique, horrible, chaud, froid, sympathique, délicieux, confortable"
    },
    "ko": {
      "title": "문법 포인트",
      "content": "• 의문사: What, Where, Who, When, Why, How\n• 목적격 대명사: me, you, him, her, it, us, them\n• this (가까운 것) / that (먼 것)\n• 형용사: 아름다운, 큰, 작은, 새로운, 오래된, 비싼, 싼, 사랑스러운, 끔찍한, 더운, 추운, 친절한, 맛있는, 편안한"
    }
  },
